OL,5, Ugandan author Kakwenza Rukirabashaija,
OL,6, who won a prestigious prize this year  
OL,7, for courageous writing, has been       
OL,8, detained, his lawyer has confirmed.    
OL,10,FThe reason for his arrest is unclear,  
OL,11,Fbut he has recently been scathing about
OL,12,FPresident Yoweri Museveni and his son  
OL,13,FLt-Gen Muhoozi Kainerugaba on Twitter. 
OL,15,FHe described the general as "obese" and
OL,16,Fsaid "the Musevenis have imposed       
OL,17,Fenormous suffering on this country".   
OL,19,FThe BBC has contacted the police for   
OL,20,Fcomment.                               
